\begin_layout Section
BOI Monetary Policy in the COVID crisis
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The main functions of the BOI are:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Managing monetary policy
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Support the activity and stability of financial markets
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Managing the foreign currency reserves of the State
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Supervising and regulating the banking system - one of the key factors that
 improves the ability to manage crises is having the monetary policy and
 the supervision of banks in a single place
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Issuing currency and regulating it
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Advising the Government on economic matters
\end_layout

